    "pid": "5d8c59ddd3761600733313ef",
    "link": "https://iiong.com",
    "comment": "<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span style=\"color: #23AC69\">import</span> {<span style=\"color: #91C132\">indexV2Api</span>} <span style=\"color: #F19726\">from</span> \"~/<span style=\"color: #E8552D\">api</span>/<span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">index</span>\";\n\n<span style=\"color: #E1147F\">export</span> <span style=\"color: #2980C1\">default</span> {\n  <span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">methods</span>: {\n    <span style=\"color: slategray\"> // 异步加载数据</span>\n     <span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">async</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">initAxiosData</span>() {\n         <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">self</span> = <span style=\"color: #A3338B\">this</span>;\n         <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">const</span> {<span style=\"color: #91C132\">data</span>} = <span style=\"color: #F19726\">await</span> <span style=\"color: #91C132\">indexV2Api</span>(<span style=\"color: #E30B20\">self</span>);\n         <span style=\"color: #E1147F\">console</span>.<span style=\"color: #2980C1\">log</span>(<span style=\"color: #91C132\">data</span>);<span style=\"color: slategray\"> // 返回接口信息</span>\n     }\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n<p><a class=\"at\" href=\"#5d8c59ddd3761600733313ef\">@Anonymous </a> , 文章说得很清楚了，引入接口调用有个参数，这个参数就是 <code>this</code> 不过我是重新指引 this 罢了。你可以直接 <code>const {data} = await indexV2Api(this)</code> 调用就行了，this 里面包含 $axios 等内置对象。</p>\n",
