    "comment": "<p><a class=\"at\" href=\"#5ed853c4ba7dda000949e866\">@yangxx.net </a> , ghost 模板暂时做不到和 WP 模板定制那么灵活，只能靠 <code>js</code> 了，你可以写个 <code>js</code> 方法如下：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">div</span> <span style=\"color: #91C132\">id</span>=\"<span style=\"color: #F19726\">demo</span>\" <span style=\"color: #E8552D\">class</span>=\"<span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">d</span>-<span style=\"color: #E1147F\">none</span>\" <span style=\"color: #2980C1\">data</span>-<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">img</span>=\"{{#<span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">if</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">feature_image</span>}}{{<span style=\"color: #E30B20\">img_url</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">feature_image</span> <span style=\"color: #A3338B\">size</span>=\"<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">l</span>\"}}{{<span style=\"color: #91C132\">else</span>}}{{'<span style=\"color: #F19726\">no</span>-<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">img</span>'}}\"&gt;&lt;/<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">div</span>&gt;&lt;!--<span style=\"color: #E1147F\">隐藏</span> <span style=\"color: #2980C1\">dom</span>--&gt;\n&lt;<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">script</span>&gt;\n<span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">function</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">randomImg</span>() {\n  <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">var</span> <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">url</span> = '<span style=\"color: #A3338B\">https</span>://<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">example</span>.<span style=\"color: #91C132\">com</span>/<span style=\"color: #F19726\">image</span>/'\n  <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">var</span> <span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">nowImg</span> = ''\n  <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">var</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">demo</span> = <span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">document</span>.<span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">getElementById</span>('<span style=\"color: #F19726\">demo</span>')\n  <span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">if</span> (<span style=\"color: #F19726\">demo</span>.<span style=\"color: #A3338B\">getAttribute</span>('<span style=\"color: #2980C1\">data</span>-<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">img</span>') === '<span style=\"color: #F19726\">no</span>-<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">img</span>') {\n    <span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">nowImg</span> = <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">url</span> + <span style=\"color: #2980C1\">Math</span>.<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">floor</span>(<span style=\"color: #2980C1\">Math</span>.<span style=\"color: #F19726\">random</span>()*<span style=\"color: #E30B20\">10</span>) + '.<span style=\"color: #E30B20\">jpg</span>'\n  } <span style=\"color: #91C132\">else</span> {\n    <span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">nowImg</span> = <span style=\"color: #F19726\">demo</span>.<span style=\"color: #A3338B\">getAttribute</span>('<span style=\"color: #2980C1\">data</span>-<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">img</span>')\n  }\n  <span style=\"color: #E1147F\">return</span> <span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">nowImg</span>\n}\n\n<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">window</span>.<span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">onload</span> = <span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">function</span>() {\n  <span style=\"color: #F19726\">randomImg</span>()\n}\n&lt;/<span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">script</span>&gt;</code></pre>\n<p>上面代码给你个扩展思考，至于能不能用我也不清楚，自行测试吧</p>\n",
