    "comment": "<p>大佬你好，想请教一下组件类型定义的问题<br>我用tsx定义了一个组件，并暴露一些方法，如下</p>\n<pre><code><span style=\"color: #23AC69\">export</span> <span style=\"color: #91C132\">default</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">defineComponent</span>({\n  <span style=\"color: #E8552D\">name</span>: '<span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">Test</span>',\n  <span style=\"color: #E1147F\">setup</span> () {\n    <span style=\"color: #2980C1\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">next</span>= () =&gt; {\n      <span style=\"color: #9FA0A0\">console</span>.<span style=\"color: #F19726\">log</span>('<span style=\"color: #E30B20\">xxx</span>')\n    }\n    <span style=\"color: #E30B20\">return</span> {\n      <span style=\"color: #1BA1E6\">next</span>\n    }\n  },\n  <span style=\"color: #23AC69\">render</span> () {...}\n})</code></pre><p>父组件代码</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">template</span>&gt;\n    &lt;<span style=\"color: #91C132\">Test</span> <span style=\"color: #F19726\">ref</span>=\"<span style=\"color: #E8552D\">testRef</span> \" /&gt;\n&lt;/<span style=\"color: #23AC69\">template</span>&gt;</code></pre><p>绑定模板中定义的ref</p>\n<pre><code><span style=\"color: #23AC69\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #91C132\">testRef</span> = <span style=\"color: #F19726\">ref</span>({} <span style=\"color: #E8552D\">as</span> <span style=\"color: #1AAB8E\">typeof</span> <span style=\"color: #E1147F\">Test</span>)</code></pre><p>然后我想在父组件输入代码<code>testRef.value.next()</code>时能有语法提示，不知道应该如何定义类型？</p>\n<p>完整的代码示例在<a href=\"https://github.com/Suzichen/vue3-ts-swiper-demo/blob/master/src/components/Demo.vue\">这里</a></p>\n<p>求帮帮萌新</p>\n",
    "url": "/vue3-use-notes/",
